+  <!--                       Should the includeSubDomains parameter be      -->
+  <!--                       included in the HSTS header.                   -->
+  <!--                                                                      -->
+  <!--   antiClickJackingEnabled                                            -->
+  <!--                       Should the anti click-jacking header           -->
+  <!--                       X-Frame-Options be added to every response?    -->
